Complaints of discrimination, harassment, and retaliation may be directed to the Office of Equal Opportunity Programs at UVaEOP@virginia.edu. Complaint procedures may be found at www.virginia.edu/eop/complaint.html. Complaints may also be filed with the Department of Education Office for Civil Rights, Equal Employment Opportunity Commission, Commonwealth of Virginia Division of Human Rights, and the Department of Human Resources Management.